onReceivedPOIs

void onReceivedPOIs(SKTrackablePOIType type,
                    java.util.List<SKDetectedPOI> detectedPOIs)
Called when the provided POIs are detected by the SKPOITrackerManager.This method is notified on the UI thread. Continuously called during a tracking session.

Parameters:
